                <expan><abbr>Aeli</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Nepos et <lb n="2"/>Dasas Arbo<lb break="no" n="3"/>nis patri caris<lb break="no" n="4"/>simo qui vixit </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> LXX <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan> memoriam <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erhalten ist der Kasten der Urne. Z. 1-4: Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata; Z. 5 darunter. (B): Patsch: Z. 2/3: Dasa Sabbo/nis.</p>
            </div>
